## 8. Performing Sensitivity Analysis
```python
# Sensitivity analysis on vendor scores
# Simple illustration of how scores change with respect to financial health
sensitivity_results = vendor_data[['Vendor_ID', 'Financial_Health_Score']].copy()
sensitivity_results['Sensitivity'] = sensitivity_results['Financial_Health_Score'].apply(lambda x: (x - 50) / 50)
sensitivity_results.head()
```

